channel.title: Client file restoration
channel.description: Okay, you know when someone removes all of the .java files from a client? well thats my problem i converted class8.java with a java decompiler, and now i got like 63 errors, does that mean i must replace every single java file or what?

item.title: Client file restoration
item.dc:creator: @Rene_eats_waffl3z Rene eats waffl3z
item.description:
@Rene_eats_waffl3z wrote:

Sanskrit:

The class8 class needs the other java files in order to import its required methods and variables. So you have to decompile all of the class files in order for it to function properly.
